H0.text: Scavengers are vultures, raccoons, and blowflies.

H1.text: Producer is what vultures, raccoons, and blowflies are examples of.

H2.text: Predator is a category that includes vultures, raccoons, and blowflies.

H3.text: Consumer are vultures, raccoons, and blowflies.

A4.text: Vultures are examples of obligate carrion scavengers.

A5.text: Raccoons feed on discarded food items.
